spec_data.Name: perl-Module-ExtractUse
spec_data.Description:
Module::ExtractUse is basically a Parse::RecDescent grammar to parse Perl
code. It tries very hard to find all modules (whether pragmas, Core, or
from CPAN) used by the parsed code.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:26:29 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Find out what modules are used
